channel.title: No-Ip error, no one can come on my server
channel.description:
Hi, It has been so many days that I never had a problem with no-ip, but today, it just stopped working. After reseting my Router. I have followed the TuT to Port Foward. Everything is as it is but no-ip still wont work.
Is there anyway, i could get it to work again (I use linksys router, though that doesnt matter, because i followed the tut and eveything is at it is supose to be)
Park~
